{"data":[{"date":"10:10 31/07","title":"\"T\u00e2n binh\" Man Utd tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb Mourinho x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/tan-binh-man-utd-trai-long-khi-bi-mourinho-xep-da-trai-keo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n hoan ngh\u00eanh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 chia b\u00e0i l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Man Utd \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Andreas Pereira c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi qua nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n \u1edf Valencia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/tan-binh-man-utd-trai-long-khi-bi-mourinho-xep-da-trai-keo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pereira c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00ecnh, anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ed9t n\u0103m qua \u1edf Valencia v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u qu\u00fd b\u00e1u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ecdc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nhanh v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n h\u01a1n, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng l\u1ed7i l\u1ea7m c\u0169 n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ed1n d\u0129 mang s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 10 ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh, gi\u1edd Pereira \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 chia b\u00e0i, m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n hoan ngh\u00eanh vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;HLV \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i n\u00f3i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadn t\u1ee5y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1. HLV h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf t\u00f4i m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Michael Carrick \u0111\u1ec1u s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean t\u00f4i trong m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, gi\u00fap t\u00f4i m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y l\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi ra th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u hay l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-truoc-mua-giai-201819-va-nu-cuoi-mim-cua-mourinho-172-192083.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-truoc-mua-giai-201819-va-nu-cuoi-mim-cua-mourinho-172-192083.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec9m c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span><br>\r\nG\u1ea1t lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m v\u1edbi Milan sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean, M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. Tuy...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-truoc-mua-giai-chet-boi-cam-bay-cua-chinh-minh-172-192305.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-truoc-mua-giai-chet-boi-cam-bay-cua-chinh-minh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-truoc-mua-giai-chet-boi-cam-bay-cua-chinh-minh-172-192305.html\">Jose Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i: Ch\u1ebft b\u1edfi c\u1ea1m b\u1eaby c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i, Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec7p kh\u00fac quen thu\u1ed9c xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. B\u1ea7u tr\u1eddi Man Utd tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb bao ph\u1ee7 b\u1edfi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1837","checkdouble":"192380"},{"date":"09:40 31/07","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-golovin-toi-monaco.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco thay v\u00ec Chelsea, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Michael Emenalo&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMichael Emenalo, c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monaco hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a Aleksandr Golovin t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-khi-Golovin-toi-Monaco-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Michael Emenalo gi\u00fap Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Emenalo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng ra quy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1edbi Monaco, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea1ch ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Michael Emenalo khi\u1ebfn Golovin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Monaco. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, song \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Monaco ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Marina Granovskaia</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marina Granovskaia l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n b\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Granovskaia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marina Granovskaia dang khong lam tot cong viec cua minh\" title=\"Marina Granovskaia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marina Granovskaia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea quan t\u00e2m Golovin tr\u01b0\u1edbc Monaco, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Marina Granovskaia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Chelsea m\u1edbi chi ra 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh, bao g\u1ed3m Jorginho v\u00e0 Robert Green. T\u00e2n HLV Sarri \u0111ang c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Rugani, Pjanic v\u00e0 Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, song \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Marina Granovskaia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong s\u1ed1 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ruben Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 Ross Barkley&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 trong th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Jorginho v\u00e0 Kante l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a The Blues.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ross Barkley co co hoi da chinh khi Chelsea khong chieu mo thanh cong Golovin\" title=\"Ross Barkley c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi Chelsea kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/bas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ross Barkley c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi Chelsea kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Golovin \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111ang c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Ruben Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 Ross Barkley c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRuben Loftus-Cheek v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea. Barkley c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Maurizio Sarri&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Chelsea ph\u1ea3i mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga. Song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri da khong the co duoc Golovin trong doi hinh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Sarri c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 38 tu\u1ed5i Robert Green.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Hazard, Willian hay Morata, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 Rugani hay Higuain \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi m\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Sarri v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 m\u00e1y Chelsea tr\u01a1n tru \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Nga</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Golovin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bong da Nga huong loi khi Golovin toi Monaco\" title=\"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea, Golovin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGolovin t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean, r\u1ea5t may \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/chinh-thuc-monaco-chieu-mo-aleksandr-golovin-197-192165.html\" target=\"_blank\">Golovin \u0111\u1ebfn Monaco</span> thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Monaco, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. HLV Jardim r\u1ea5t m\u00e1t tay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Leonardo Jardim&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leonardo Jardim \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u00d4ng bi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, Monaco t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leonardo Jardim lai co mot cau thu tiem nang de nhao nhan thanh sao lon\" title=\"Leonardo Jardim l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0o nh\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh sao l\u1edbn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/hlv.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leonardo Jardim l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0o nh\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh sao l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u01a1n 400 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Kylian Mbappe, Fabinho, Thomas Lemar, Benjamin Mendy, Bernardo Silva v\u00e0 Tiemoue Bakayoko.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Golovin h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Leonardo Jardim l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n Monaco ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Golovin trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n*Squawka</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1836","checkdouble":"192381"},{"date":"10:13 31/07","title":"HLV Leicester n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/hlv-leicester-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-mu-chieu-mo-maguire.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw 01h30 ng\u00e0y 18 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw 01h30 ng\u00e0y 18 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Spartak_Trnava_vs_Legia_Warsaw.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Legia Warszawa d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Cork City, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch CH Ireland, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0. Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ba Lan khi h\u1ecd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Spartak Trnava ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 0-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLegia \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 r\u1eddi r\u1ea1c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ba Lan \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u1edbi 3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh trang t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Spartak Trnava h\u00f4m nay, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Spartak Trnava, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Slovakia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua. 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Spartak Trnava ch\u1ec9 thua 1 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n 9/13 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, Legia Warszawa ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Spartak Trnava do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 thi tri\u1ec3n l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Tin v\u00e0o th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ti\u1ebfp theo cho Spartak Trnava \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nSpartak Trnava: M. Chudy, M. Toth, M. Conka, I. Hladik, B. Godal, A. Kadlec, E. Grendel, J. Rada, L. Gressak, E. Jirka, M. Egho<br>\r\nLegia Warszawa: Skaba Brzyski, Dossa, Junior, Rzezniczak, Bereszynski, Furman, Jodlowiec, Kosecki, Helio Pinto, Kucharczyk, Dvalishvili</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1835","checkdouble":"192382"},{"date":"10:42 31/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ea9u v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/huyen-thoai-mu-tiep-tuc-dau-khau-voi-tan-binh-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi b\u1ecb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri gay g\u1eaft \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Gary Neville quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 y\u00ean khi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch s\u1eb7c m\u00f9i ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0n em.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng r\u1ebb nh\u01b0 cho so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, vi\u1ec7c Xherdan Shaqiri t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n sau khi Stoke City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Premier League.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/huyen-thoai-mu-tiep-tuc-dau-khau-voi-tan-binh-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i v\u00ec s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Shaqiri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i anh v\u1eabn b\u1ecb <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-buong-loi-dap-tra-khi-bi-huyen-thoai-mu-chui-thang-mat-172-192056.html\" target=\"_blank\">anh em nh\u00e0 Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p</span> v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng to\u00e0n t\u00e2m to\u00e0n \u00fd cho Stoke, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ra \u0111i cho d\u1ec5 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Man Utd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1edbi m\u00f3c v\u1edb v\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cd\u00ecm h\u00e0ng\u201d \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Liverpool, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 IC Cup 2018, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Man Utd \u0111\u1ebfn 4-1, v\u1edbi Shaqiri ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00fa xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u1ed5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Gary Neville c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed3m mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n em thua k\u00e9m g\u1ea7n 20 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Shaqiri ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n Ronaldinho th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 hay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u1eadu ta th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebfng, ch\u1ec9 th\u00edch \u0111\u1ee9ng y\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u1ed7 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u00edch Shaqiri, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Xin ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu ta ra sao v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Stoke xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\u201d</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1834","checkdouble":"192383"},{"date":"10:24 31/07","title":"HLV HAGL tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV HAGL \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>HLV HAGL tin h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV HAGL tin h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV HAGL tin h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n HAGL D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, \u0111a s\u1ed1 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, cho n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd \u1ed5n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u00f4i, \u1edf l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i U23, c\u00e1c HAGL s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 HAGL n\u00f3i ri\u00eang. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 khung t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ASIAD 18. Suy cho c\u00f9ng c\u00e1i \u0111\u00edch m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c thay v\u00ec m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t\u201d, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o Bongdaplus.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat lo ng\u1ea1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t sau khi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat lo l\u1eafng l\u00e0 m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. C\u0169ng n\u00ean nh\u1edb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, V-League ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c trung b\u00ecnh 1 tu\u1ea7n kho\u1ea3ng 2 tr\u1eadn trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sau nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3 t\u1ea1i V-League, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duoc-thay-park-ngoi-khen-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sang-cua-bat-chinh-168-192379.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/duoc-thay-park-ngoi-khen-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sang-cua-bat-chinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duoc-thay-park-ngoi-khen-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sang-cua-bat-chinh-168-192379.html\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park ng\u1ee3i khen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1833","checkdouble":"192384"},{"date":"10:43 31/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw 01h30 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-spartak-trnava-vs-legia-warsaw-01h30-ngay-18-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw 01h30 ng\u00e0y 18 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw 01h30 ng\u00e0y 18 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Spartak_Trnava_vs_Legia_Warsaw.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Legia Warszawa d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Cork City, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch CH Ireland, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0. Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ba Lan khi h\u1ecd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Spartak Trnava ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 0-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLegia \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 r\u1eddi r\u1ea1c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ba Lan \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u1edbi 3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh trang t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Spartak Trnava h\u00f4m nay, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Spartak Trnava, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Slovakia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua. 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Spartak Trnava ch\u1ec9 thua 1 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n 9/13 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, Legia Warszawa ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Spartak Trnava do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 thi tri\u1ec3n l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Tin v\u00e0o th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ti\u1ebfp theo cho Spartak Trnava \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nSpartak Trnava: M. Chudy, M. Toth, M. Conka, I. Hladik, B. Godal, A. Kadlec, E. Grendel, J. Rada, L. Gressak, E. Jirka, M. Egho<br>\r\nLegia Warszawa: Skaba Brzyski, Dossa, Junior, Rzezniczak, Bereszynski, Furman, Jodlowiec, Kosecki, Helio Pinto, Kucharczyk, Dvalishvili</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1832","checkdouble":"192385"},{"date":"10:48 31/07","title":"Sau ASIAD, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi VTV tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AFF Cup v\u00ec m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vtv-co-mua-ban-quyen-aff-cup-2018-0133c047.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb ch\u00e0o gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AFF Cup 2018 qu\u00e1 cao khi\u1ebfn VTV ch\u00f9n b\u01b0\u1edbc</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang t\u0103ng phi m\u00e3, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang t\u0103ng ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 EURO, World Cup m\u00e0 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c, ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u0169ng h\u00f2a chung xu th\u1ebf n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi VTV tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD, \u0111ang r\u1ed9 l\u00ean tin \u0111\u1ed3n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 khi b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i AFF Cup \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o b\u00e1n qu\u00e1 cao. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh AFF Cup 2018 - gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u00ec n\u0103m 2016. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2018, VTV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 tri\u1ec7u USD. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 phi l\u00fd cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 khu v\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu VTV kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto-Regular, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\">VTV tu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018: Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 do ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t cao khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1831","checkdouble":"192386"},{"date":"11:11 31/07","title":"Bayern Munich b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n sao cho MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/10/bayern-munich-bo-ngo-kha-nang-ban-sao-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i \u1edf Allianz Arena v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 Arturo Vidal ra \u0111i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-duc/tan-hlv-bayern-munich-da-deu-tbn-trong-ngay-ra-mat-193-190306.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Bayern Munich, t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac</span> quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5, d\u1ecdn s\u1ea1ch t\u00e0n t\u00edch th\u1eeba th\u00e3i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Pep Guardiola v\u00e0 Carlo Ancelotti. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n thanh l\u00fd l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Arturo Vidal, tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t su\u1ed1t bao n\u0103m qua \u1edf Allianz Arena.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Vidal cho MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern Munich b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Vidal cho MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/10/MU-mua-Arturo-Vidal-voi-gia-26-trieu-bang-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern Munich b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Vidal cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i v\u1eady th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 31 xem ra v\u1eabn c\u00f2n mang r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb trong m\u1eaft c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0 Inter Milan hay \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Man Utd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n anh t\u1eeb th\u1eddi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia khi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i \u1edf Bayern Munich v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 Vidal ra \u0111i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m x\u1ee9 Bavaria\u201d:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u0111i n\u00f3i l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang d\u01b0 th\u1eeba 1-2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. HLV l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f3 x\u1eed v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 v\u00e0 lo chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u1edf n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 CLB mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Vidal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich n\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh ra \u0111i trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Man Utd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd vi\u1ec7n nh\u1edd ng\u00f4i sao Alexis Sanchez d\u00f9ng t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Chile v\u1ec1 h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 \u1edf Old Trafford.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-arturo-vidal-sap-ky-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-191920.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/vidal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-arturo-vidal-sap-ky-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-191920.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Bayern Munich trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bayern-bao-gia-mua-vidal-cho-2-dai-gia-thanh-milan-176-191832.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/5/bayern-bao-gia-mua-vidal-cho-2-dai-gia-thanh-milan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bayern-bao-gia-mua-vidal-cho-2-dai-gia-thanh-milan-176-191832.html\">Bayern b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 mua Vidal cho \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan</span><br>\r\nBayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 ra gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1830","checkdouble":"192388"},{"date":"11:14 31/07","title":"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Simeone n\u00f3i \u0111\u00fang, Ronaldo gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n Messi!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/quan-diem-simeone-noi-dung-ronaldo-gia-tri-hon-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u00d4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn CR7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00f2n Leo th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Simeone l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n gi\u1eefa Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi, ai h\u01a1n ai l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o gi\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 n\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch say m\u00ea v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft ch\u00e1n. Sau c\u00f9ng, <em>Ronaldo c\u00f3 hay h\u01a1n Messi hay kh\u00f4ng, m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ef1 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn</em>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBongda24h.vn c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a ra quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i l\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng li\u00ean k\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/iniesta-chia-tay-barca-messi-con-no-anh-2-qua-bong-vang-180-186764.html\">Iniesta chia tay Barca: Messi c\u00f2n n\u1ee3 anh 2 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-toa-sang-tran-dau-juventus-vs-real-madrid-va-su-kho-chiu-cua-messi-184-183504.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ronaldo h\u00f3a &ldquo;Th\u00e1nh&rdquo;, ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-gianh-qua-bong-vang-2017-khong-chi-ngang-messi-180-174863.html\">Ronaldo gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng 2017: S\u00e1nh ngang Messi? \u1ed2 kh\u00f4ng&hellip;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f9ng <strong>nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi</strong>. M\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh ri\u00eang v\u00e0 t\u1ef1u chung h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, <u>d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 Simeone, \u00f4ng th\u00edch Ronaldo h\u01a1n</u>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Ronaldo-va-Messi-qua-nx-Simeone.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Simeone, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu ch\u1ec9 1 trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i oan gia Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ch\u00e2n s\u00fat v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid. V\u1edbi <strong>Messi, anh ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i hay khi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh</strong> v\u00e0 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e3y th\u1eed \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ecba v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Simeone, ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1c. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u1ec1 th\u1ebf nh\u01b0 Barca. <em>\u0110\u1eb7t Messi sang b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c</em> ngo\u00e0i g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia, <em>anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u00ecm ngh\u1ec9m v\u00e0 Ronaldo th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i</em>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/giua-messi-va-ronaldo-simeone-chon-ai-xuat-sac-hon-180-192278.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/giua-messi-va-ronaldo-simeone-chon-ai-xuat-sac-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/giua-messi-va-ronaldo-simeone-chon-ai-xuat-sac-hon-180-192278.html\">Gi\u1eefa Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo, Simeone ch\u1ecdn ai xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n?</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo. \u00d4ng cho r\u1eb1ng trong m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao, Lionel Messi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nRonaldo gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n Messi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, <u>Messi \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u00ean t\u00e0i theo \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a \u0111en</u>. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng tr\u1eddi ph\u00fa cho nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai mu\u1ed1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3. Ronaldo c\u00f3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng, h\u00e0ng n\u0103m c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m cho m\u00ecnh s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m th\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao l\u1edbn l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Messi. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111i nh\u01b0 bay m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n n\u1ed5i. Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn <em>ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n x\u00e9t tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n</em>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va Messi\" title=\"Ronaldo va Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Ronaldo-va-Messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Simeone tin Ronaldo to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n Messi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Argentina, Simeone c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt: <strong>Messi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3</strong>. M\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u00ec l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao n\u1eb7ng t\u00ednh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i tennis, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Messi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0i nh\u01b0 Roger Federer hay Rafael Nadal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, <u>Messi kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</u>. M\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng \u0110T Argentina v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Leo c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu. \u0110\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 Tango c\u0169ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00f3i tr\u00ean. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd xem Messi \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Diego Maradona, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0a Argentina t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1986.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi that vong Argentina\" title=\"Messi that vong Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Messi-that-vong-Argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Leo n\u1ee3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi \u0111\u1ea1t 9, 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi ch\u01a1i cho Barcelona th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 6, 7 khi l\u00ean Argentina. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a anh. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 Tango nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua lu\u00f4n n\u1edf r\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c Mauro Icardi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, Paulo Dybala ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Argentina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u1eb1m \u1edf anh</strong>. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i di\u1ec5n ra, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch gom to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Barca l\u00ean s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng Leo \u1edf \u0110TQG, m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-chung-kien-ronaldo-thi-dau-chu-de-messi-co-buon-421-189520.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/goc-nhin-chung-kien-ronaldo-thi-dau-chu-de-messi-co-buon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-chung-kien-ronaldo-thi-dau-chu-de-messi-co-buon-421-189520.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u, &ldquo;ch\u00fa d\u00ea&rdquo; Messi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed3n?</span><br>\r\n<span>L\u00e0 c\u1eb7p k\u1ef3 ph\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong 10 n\u0103m qua, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa 2 si\u00eau nh\u00e2n n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i s\u1ef1...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou, Messi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 su\u1ed1t 17 n\u0103m qua. T\u1eeb khi m\u1edbi 14 tu\u1ed5i, c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean Barca \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra Messi, \u0111\u01b0a anh t\u1eeb Argentina t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o. Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat xa l\u1ea1 n\u00e0o v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca khi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 b\u1edfi h\u1ed3n c\u1ed1t Tiki-Taka xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 th\u1ebf, khi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1, <u>Messi c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</u>. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t, anh ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Ronaldinho, Thierry Henry, Samuel Eto'o, Xavi, Andres Iniesta, David Villa, Zlatan Ibrahimovic, Neymar v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Luis Suarez, Phil Coutinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du Messi chi vao san tu bang ghe du bi\" title=\"D\u00f9 Messi ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/18/tong-hop-celta-vigo-22-barca-vong-33-la-liga-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 &quot;\u00f4ng vua con&quot; t\u1ea1i Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<u>T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t hay v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho Messi</u>. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u00e9p ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i tr\u00e1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hay tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00e2n s\u1ee7ng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Barca d\u00e0nh cho Messi. \u1ede m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Messi c\u00f3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i qua kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i</strong> nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Andorinha v\u00e0 Nacional t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 kinh qua 3 CLB bao g\u1ed3m Sporting Lisbon (B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha), Man United (Anh), Real Madrid (T\u00e2y Ban Nha) v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>T\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u, Ronaldo c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t</em>. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u1ecdi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng, ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo nha chinh phuc cac danh hieu\" title=\"Ronaldo nha chinh phuc cac danh hieu\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Juventus-chieu-mo-Cristiano-Ronaldo-Co-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo d\u00e1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi c\u00f2n Messi th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7t gi\u1ea3 thi\u1ebft Simeone \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn s\u1edf h\u1eefu ho\u1eb7c Ronaldo ho\u1eb7c Messi cho Atletico Madrid. Tin ch\u1eafc, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 qu\u00fd m\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5y, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn Messi cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u00f4i sao cao 1m70 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Inter Milan n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Barca, song t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng \u1edf l\u1eddi n\u00f3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i l\u1ea1i. V\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi k\u00fd cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, <u>tr\u1ecdn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Messi s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou</u>. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y anh ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thay v\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u01b0u \u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t su\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf m\u1edbi n\u00f3i <em>Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n Ronaldo th\u00ec c\u00f3</em>. \u0110\u1ebfn Argentina v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, Leo c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c c\u01a1 m\u00e0&hellip;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/neymar-va\u0300-messi-hit-khoi-ronaldo-ve-thu-nhap-tren-instagram-188-192144.html\">Neymar va\u0300 Messi 'h\u00edt kh\u00f3i' Ronaldo v\u1ec1 thu nh\u1eadp tr\u00ean Instagram</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/danh-sach-cau-thu-hay-nhat-nam-cua-fifa-mbappe-sanh-vai-cung-ronaldo-messi-184-191953.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a FIFA: Mbappe s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Ronaldo, Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi-180-191515.html\">N\u1ebfu Ronaldo l\u00e0 Nadal, Messi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Federer</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mourinho-ronaldo-se-phuc-hung-bong-da-y-176-191396.html\">Mourinho: &ldquo;Ronaldo s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi-184-191064.html\">Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00ec&hellip; Messi?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1829","checkdouble":"192389"},{"date":"11:18 31/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 31/7: Everton ch\u1ed3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/16/ngay-hom-nay-317.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (31/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>Everton ch\u1ed3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\nHLV Marco Silva t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Marcos Rojo t\u1ea1i Sporting Lisbon tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1ecb HLV n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Argentina t\u1ea1i Everton. Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail (Anh), Everton \u0111\u00e3 duy\u1ec7t chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Rojo. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00f3n t\u00e2n binh.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 317, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 317, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/16/MU-CHINH-THUC-troi-chan-thanh-cong-tru-cot-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marcos Rojo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ee5 Courtois sang Real</h2>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin uy t\u00edn t\u1eeb Sky Sports kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n b\u00e1n Thibaut Courtois cho Real Madrid. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m \u1edf m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \"Los Blancos\" \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb (\u0111ang l\u00e0 32 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) m\u00e0 \"The Blues\" mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f2n theo Mirror, Jack Butland c\u1ee7a Stoke City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge li\u00ean h\u1ec7.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-khien-real-van-chua-the-cong-bo-bom-tan-courtois-172-192377.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 bom t\u1ea5n Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Fulham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mitrovic</h2>\r\n<p>Th\u00e1ng  1/2018, Aleksandar Mitrovic t\u1edbi Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Newcastle.  Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 17 tr\u1eadn m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i  b\u00f3ng London th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00ean ch\u01a1i \u1edf Premier League. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, Fulham ch\u00ednh  th\u1ee9c k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 23 tu\u1ed5i. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n  nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00ean ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a ESPN, n\u00f3 r\u01a1i  v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 20-22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 317 Everton ch\u1ed3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 317 Everton ch\u1ed3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-317-Everton-chong-30-trieu-bang-mua-Marcos-Rojo-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mitrovic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>Juventus v\u00e0 Milan trao \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain v\u00e0 Bonucci</h2>\r\nGoal \u0111\u01b0a tin, anh trai ki\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Gonzalo Higuain - Nicolas \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 t\u00e2n gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a AC Milan - Leonardo \u0111\u1ec3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \"El Pipita\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, AC Milan s\u1ebd m\u01b0\u1ee3n Higuain 1 m\u00f9a v\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed 18 tri\u1ec7u euro tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u1ee9t anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00e8 2019. \u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, \"Rossoneri\" c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Leonardo Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Juventus d\u00f9 anh m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro gia nh\u1eadp n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf - \u0111en th\u00e0nh Milano \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 n\u0103m do trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf San Siro.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-va-ac-milan-sap-trao-doi-bom-tan-176-191928.html\">Juventus v\u00e0 AC Milan s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Marseille mu\u1ed1n Giroud h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng thay Balotelli</h2>\r\nSau khi kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat l\u1eafm t\u00e0i nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd Mario Balotelli gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh do b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng, Olympique de Marseille \u0111\u00e3 quay sang ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p Olivier Giroud.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00e2n s\u00fat v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Chelsea. Theo t\u1edd Mirror, Marseille s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Giroud h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1828","checkdouble":"192390"},{"date":"07:48 31/07","title":"\"Silva \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/silva-dang-trong-giai-doan-tot-nhat-cua-su-nghiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1i t\u00ean David \u2013 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Villa ca ng\u1ee3i Silva \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng tuy\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nVilla h\u1ebft l\u1eddi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Silva<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft trong 5 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Valencia, 2 ch\u00e0ng David g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2008 v\u00e0 World Cup 2010. \u0110\u1ebfn nay, c\u1ea3 2 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m chung n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi HLV Pep Guardiola t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c nhau (Barca v\u00e0 Man City).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do David Villa hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi Pep c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Man City v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. David Silva v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Villa ca ng\u1ee3i Silva \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Pep\" title=\"David Silva nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb HLV Pep Guardiola.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/silva-dang-trong-giai-doan-tot-nhat-cua-su-nghiep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Villa ca ng\u1ee3i Silva \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Pep</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n sang Barca. Khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Champions League c\u00f9ng Valencia, nh\u01b0ng Pep \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft David Silva khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1ea1i Valencia. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 s\u1ebd hay h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd thay \u0111\u1ed5i tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o, c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Man City. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a David, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu con trai c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. David n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 th\u00eam v\u00e0i n\u0103m n\u1eefa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Villa ca ng\u1ee3i Silva.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/david-silva-can-nhac-chia-tay-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-192262.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/david-silva-can-nhac-chia-tay-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/david-silva-can-nhac-chia-tay-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-192262.html\">David Silva c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf</span><br>\r\nDavid Silva c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 xem x\u00e9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-23-man-city-icc-2018-329-192238.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-23-man-city-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-23-man-city-icc-2018-329-192238.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Bayern Munich 2-3 Man City (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb c\u00f2n v\u00f4 danh \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd. C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1ed9c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1827","checkdouble":"192364"},{"date":"07:17 31/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sheriff vs Shkendija 00h00 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-sheriff-vs-shkendija-00h00-ngay-18-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sheriff vs Shkendija l\u00fac 00h00 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sheriff vs Shkendija 00h00 ng\u00e0y 18 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sheriff vs Shkendija 00h00 ng\u00e0y 18 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Sheriff-vs-Shkendija.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sheriff vs Shkendija</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Sheriff vs Shkendija: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Sheriff \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Macedonia (0-1). Th\u1ef1c ra \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1edfi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Goran Sabli\u0107 v\u1ed1n y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng v\u00eda khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a FC Torpedo Kutaisi, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Georgia (1-2). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i Sheriff s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau khi g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 1-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a FC Torpedo Kutaisi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i s\u00e0o huy\u1ec7t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Sheriff th\u1eafng theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khi ti\u1ebfp kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. T\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Sabli\u0107 mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui \u1edf 8/9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p TLCA<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 Sheriff \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Shkendija. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu Sheriff ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1826","checkdouble":"192365"},{"date":"07:32 31/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Hapoel Beer Sheva vs Dinamo Zagreb 00h00 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-hapoel-beer-sheva-vs-dinamo-zagreb-00h00-ngay-18-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u2013 Charlie Adam, anh tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAdam t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 Liverpool<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ra. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB l\u00e0 Charlie Adam cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 1 trong 2 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Klopp bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t bom t\u1ea5n trong khung g\u1ed7. Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 6-8 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Liverpool trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Charlie Adam tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League\" title=\"charlie adam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2012/7/Charlie-Adam-Hairstyles-500x375-201271674631.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Charlie Adam tin r\u1eb1ng&nbsp;Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Shaqiri, m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu Mohamed Salah c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thay th\u1ebf cho Salah, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd Shaqiri s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Shaqiri s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Liverpool, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Charlie Adam chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Kop, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Stoke City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-172-192321.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-172-192321.html\">Van Dijk: Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Liverpool, Mourinho \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho&hellip; Martial</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng b\u1ecb m\u1eafng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Martial v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1825","checkdouble":"192366"},{"date":"08:43 31/07","title":"Petr Cech \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 Leno: \"Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi Bundesliga\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/petr-cech-dap-tra-leno-ngoai-hang-anh-khac-han-so-voi-bundesliga.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno, ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leno quy\u1ebft\u00a0 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Petr Cech</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 5 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ph\u1ea3i chi ra 19.3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Petr-Cech-phat-bieu-ve-Bernd-Leno-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leno mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Cech</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-19-trieu-bang-len-tieng-canh-bao-petr-cech-172-192297.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bernd Leno kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi Petr Cech</span> cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cAnh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y, t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u1eaft HLV. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 run s\u1ee3. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh gi\u1eefa t\u00f4i, Cech v\u00e0 Ospina gi\u00fap Arsenal ti\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Petr Cech l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno, ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petr Cech phat bieu ve Leno\" title=\"Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/petr-cech-dap-tra-leno-ngoai-hang-anh-khac-han-so-voi-bundesliga.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh\u00a0c\u00f4ng \u1edf Premier League. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede Premier League, m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Leno \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1824","checkdouble":"192367"},{"date":"09:01 31/07","title":"Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/willian-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-va-real-madrid.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Conte song th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ghi 7 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 20 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Willian-noi-ve-tuong-lai-truoc-tin-don-duoc-MU-va-Real-quan-tam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m Willian\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 khi\u1ebfn Mourinho th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea mu\u1ed1n M.U chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-muon-chi-100-trieu-bang-cho-courtois-va-willian-180-192290.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian</span>, Los Blancos th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Courtois v\u00e0 Willian. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef Willian \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song Chelsea c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay th\u1ebf trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Pulisic c\u1ee7a Dortmund trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Willian ra \u0111i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Willian kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n Willian \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018, anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Chelsea. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Stamford Bridge \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" title=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/chelsea-dong-y-ban-willian-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nWillian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Brazil, Esporte Espetacular, Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Chelsea h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i\u00a0r\u1ea5t vui \u1edf Chelsea, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi s\u1ed1ng \u1edf London\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Willian, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111ang r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia coi ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1823","checkdouble":"192368"}]}